Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:23.70,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}どこにもいけない それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:28.86,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}Just tell me now please tell me now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:32.98,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}まだここにいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:36.42,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}枯れそうな花 ひとりきりでも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.94,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}I'm dreaming 'bout you every night
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:43.70,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}but you're not by my side
