Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:18.42,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}終らない世界にだって立ち向かうように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:24.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover 命の声がまた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:30.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}響きだす頃に あなたと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:36.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}沈まずに行く船を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:23.40,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}踏入shadow land 才不是樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:28.66,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}Sappy old remedies 無法確定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.83,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}即使如此 go up the river
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:35.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}咬緊牙關 became a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.08,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}連有眼涙都宛如燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.84,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}一個sign 一個light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:47.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願沒有黎明的夜晚 歌聲不會間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:53.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願不要困在和彷徨迷惑的夢境裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:59.65,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願交錯的足跡們不再執著過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:06.07,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願就算你一旦失足 也千萬別放手
