Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:18.42,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願能勇敢面對沒有結束的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:24.26,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover 生命的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:30.89,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}還在發出聲響 與你一起
